Package uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.serial

Provides parsers and renders for the XML serialisation of MEKON model instantiations, plus renderers for CFrame hierarchies.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CHierarchyParser
    Parser for the standard XML serialisation of section of CFrame-hierarchy.
    CHierarchyRenderer
    Renderer for the standard XML serialisation of section of CFrame-hierarchy.
    CIdentitySerialiser
    Provides a set of utility methods for the serialisation of CIdentity objects to/from configuration files.
    IInstanceParseInput
    Represents the input-data for a specific IFrame/ISlot network parsing operation to be performed by a IInstanceParser, including structures into which certain output-data may be written.
    IInstanceParser
    Parser for the standard XML serialisation of MEKON instances as represented via IFrame/ISlot networks.
    IInstanceRenderer
    Renderer for the standard XML serialisation of MEKON instances as represented via IFrame/ISlot networks.
    IInstanceRenderInput
    Represents the input-data for a specific IFrame/ISlot network rendering operation to be performed by a IInstanceRenderer, including structures into which certain output-data may be written.
